---
// WhyUs.astro
---

<section id="whyus" class="relative w-full mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-32 py-16 md:py-32">
    <!-- Background Elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-40 right-0 w-72 md:w-96 h-72 md:h-96 bg-accentColor/30 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-52 md:w-72 h-52 md:h-72 bg-accentColor/60 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 md:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 md:mb-6">Why Choose Us</h2>
      <div class="w-16 md:w-20 h-1 bg-accentColor rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Cards Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
      <!-- Card 01 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">01.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Delivery Quality</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          Successful campaigns are built on high-quality, highly focused work. We deliver digital marketing 
          campaigns using data-driven insights to bring our clients real success.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 02 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">02.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Integrate to Innovate</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          Our integrated team approach ensures we're in it together, bringing our clients innovative 
          solutions from our wide range of skills and experience.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 03 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">03.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Determine Approach</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          All of our efforts go into delivering the best for our clients, driving their businesses forward. 
          This determination continuously drives us to overcome challenges and go above and beyond.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 04 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">04.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Total Transparency</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          Everything we do is with a commitment to transparency, providing open and honest communication. 
          We work seamlessly as an extension of our client's internal teams.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 05 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">05.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Independent Vision</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          As an independent digital agency, we break free from restrictions and limitations. Working with 
          creative freedom, we deliver results that match our clients' unique goals.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Card 06 -->
      <div class="group p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gray-800 
                  hover:border-accentColor/50 transition-all duration-300">
        <p class="text-accentColor font-mono text-base md:text-lg mb-3 md:mb-4">06.</p>
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 md:mb-4">Provide Clarity</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
          Clear and simple, we provide clarity from start to finish so that every opportunity and challenge 
          can be explored and explained, putting our clients on a path to success.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
</section>